    <item>
      <title>维尔德斯不会成为荷兰总理，但仍然可以成为国王拥护者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/wilders-won-t-become-dutch-premier-but-can-still-be-kingmaker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔特·维尔德斯 (Geert Wilders) 和他的联盟竞争对手同意讨论一种政府形式，党派领导人仍留在议会，但不加入内阁，一天前，这位极右翼议员放弃了成为荷兰首相的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/wilders-won-t-become-dutch-premier-but-can-still-be-kingmaker</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 16:42:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰反对派要求法院阻止央行行长调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/polish-opposition-asks-court-to-block-central-bank-chief-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰民族主义反对派正在尽最后努力阻止对央行行长进行有争议的调查，议会最早可能于下周开始进行调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/polish-opposition-asks-court-to-block-central-bank-chief-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 16:15:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒默呼吁以色列举行大选 与内塔尼亚胡决裂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/schumer-calls-for-elections-in-israel-in-break-with-netanyahu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院多数党领袖查克·舒默呼吁以色列举行新的选举，这与美国最高级别的犹太民选官员总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的立场截然不同。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/schumer-calls-for-elections-in-israel-in-break-with-netanyahu</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 15:03:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加州无家可归者计划的失败对纽瑟姆来说是一个警告信号</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/california-s-prop-1-winning-by-tight-margin-is-bad-for-newsom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州一项旨在授权州长加文·纽瑟姆减少无家可归者计划的一项重要内容的投票措施有望获得通过，但微弱的优势表明对其议程的支持有所减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/california-s-prop-1-winning-by-tight-margin-is-bad-for-newsom</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>因加沙抗议而被暂停的团体起诉哥伦比亚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/columbia-sued-by-students-groups-suspended-over-gaza-war-protest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚大学因反对加沙战争的示威活动而被两个学生团体起诉，这两个团体去年被停课，这是该校因反犹太主义和巴勒斯坦权利等热门话题而面临的越来越多诉讼中的最新一起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/columbia-sued-by-students-groups-suspended-over-gaza-war-protest</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 16:55:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
